snippet.title: KOPPOTATE’S RESCUE MISSION 2: THE PATH TO ERADICATION - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Join Koppotate, Ruby and A.J. on a journey to save Koppai from a terrible pandemic. Explore lush environments and brand-new custom story mode maps as you progress towards the eradication of this virus! Koppotate’s Rescue Mission 2: The Path to Eradication will release sometime in the future, with a date TBD. A Demo will be available soon!
